[src:biomaterials/titanium-biocompatibility] This simulation is a good approximation of adsorption to a surface when compared to experimental values.
[src:biomaterials/titanium-biocompatibility] The Langmuir isotherm for adsorption of elements onto the titanium surface can be determined by plotting the know parameters.
